Welcome Home: (Location/Location/Location) This 2,348 square feet, 3 bedroom, 2.25-bathroom quality built home is situated on a large lot with a fully fenced, landscaped back yard and across the street is a community tennis/pickle ball court. Home boasts of a gas forced air furnace, gas range, a heat pump, covered front porch, large family room (with pool table) and more. Only minutes from downtown Poulsbo for great shopping and entertainment. In summary, this 3-bedroom, 2.25-bathroom home is a testament to quality craftsmanship and comfortable living. With its thoughtful amenities, spacious layout, and prime location, it's an ideal place to call home.
